		{"id":"f614ab35ea5feef6","type":"text","text":"```cpp\ntemplate <typename T, size_t N>\nstruct RingBuffer {\n\tstd::array<T, N> data;\n\tsize_t write_idx = 0;\n\tsize_t read_idx = 0;\n\tstd::atomic<size_t> count{0};\n\tbool is_full() const { return count.load() >= N; }                                                             \n\tbool is_empty() const { return count.load() == 0; }                                                                                                 \n\tvoid push() {\n\t\twrite_idx = (write_idx + 1) % N;\n\t\tcount.fetch_add(1);\n\t}\n\t\n\tvoid pop() {\n\t\tread_idx = (read_idx + 1) % N;\n\t\tcount.fetch_sub(1);\n\t}\n};\n```\n","x":-320,"y":-840,"width":560,"height":520},
